style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Hello =
Raffaella,</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">Thank you for the email below.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">We can confirm that =
testing can commence at 2pm on Friday October =
17.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">We =
will test from sample sites as required to complete a full and thorough =
determination of any potential contamination, inclusive of all the areas =
which you have referred to below.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">You may undertake your own =
independent testing at any stage; however, Tower would only consider =
reimbursement for testing which is - a) claim related &amp; b) testing =
which is outside of that which Tower will complete.<span =
class=3D"Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I am confident that the =
Tower Insurance testing will be transparent, quantified by lab results, =
and adequate to provide comfort for all =
parties.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><u><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Clarified scope of testing as =
follows:</span></u><o:p></o:p></div><ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1" =
style=3D"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in;"><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">150mm =
diameter inspection portals cut in wall cavities of every room on the =
first floor at a height of 300 mm of floor level and directly underneath =
the top plate.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Testing of the roof cavity =
at the soffit junction where potential contaminants may have risen =
through the wall cavity. Testing of the roof cavity at the apex where =
smoke may have accumulated.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">Testing of the underside of the rear large upper =
deck.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Testing of the basement =
utilizing all exposed framing cavities and 150mm testing portals cut =
into any remining ceiling linings in the basemen =
area.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Any additional sample =
sites that we feel are required during testing. =
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><u><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">To ensure effectual =
testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the =
following:</span></u><o:p></o:p></div><ol start=3D"4" type=3D"1" =
style=3D"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in;"><li =
class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; =
font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">That =
the chlorine was located in the laundry room downstairs at the time of =
the fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">The quantity of the =
chlorine that was in that room at the time of the =
fire.</span><o:p></o:p></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Where there any<span =
class=3D"Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>other chemicals</u><span =
class=3D"Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that were located in that =
same room, or anywhere else downstairs. =
&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></li></ol><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Beyond completing testing =
and providing laboratory results as described above, I am certain the =
most productive action we can make towards progressing the claim is to =
have a meeting where we can discuss the overall claim response process, =
providing a forum for you to table any questions, or concerns that you =
may hold. Those concerns can be responded to, and the responses can be =
documented via minutes with actions and agreements detailed in the =
minutes providing a framework for moving forward with a pre-agreed and =
productive pathway. I believe this would be very worthwhile and will =
provide us all with detail, clarity, and documentation that we can all =
use to our benefit.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Your lawyers and advisors would of course be =
welcome to attend this meeting.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I look forward to seeing you again on =
Friday.</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: =
12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">Kind Regards,</span><o:p></o:p></div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Grant. =
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div><d=
