style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Having reviewed =
the proposed plan, I=E2=80=99m concerned the current testing schedule =
appears incomplete. It does not include the first floor, roof cavity, or =
the large upper deck, and the basement coverage seems partial, given the =
known extent of smoke, water, and chemical =
contamination.<o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">I therefore =
request confirmation that the planned inspection and sampling will be =
expanded to include all levels and relevant structural areas. =
Alternatively, please confirm that Tower will meet my reasonable costs =
should I need to arrange independent specialists to carry out =
supplementary testing (including laboratory =
analysis).<o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
