style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Hello Raffaella and =
Abigail,</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Thank you for the letter received yesterday =
at 4:35</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I am replying to acknowledge receipt of the =
letter, and to further acknowledge that Abigail will be copied into all =
correspondence moving forward.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I have requested that the =
appointed specialists provide dates and times when they can be =
available.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I am proposing that the following persons =
complete site visit, assessing &amp; testing, as a necessary =
pre-requisite to providing relevant reports for all stakeholders to =
review:</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><b><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Grant =
Metson</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">=E2=80=93 Regional Assessing =
Manager</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Stephen Walker</span></b><span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">=E2=80=93 =
Technical Building Consultant. =
ASURNZ.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Warwick Banks</span></b><span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">=E2=80=93 =
Associate Structural Engineer. =
CPEng</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Alexandra Dalzell</span></b><span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">=E2=80=93 =
Forensic Scientist</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin:=
 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Tyrell Craig</span></b><span =
class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">=E2=80=93 =
Restoration Cleaning Specialist.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><b><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">LBP =
Builder</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">[ unconfirmed individual ] =E2=80=93 we will require the builder =
to cut inspection holes in the wall linings so testing can be completed =
within the wall cavities.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: =
11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: =
0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">The intention is to test for smoke and =
chemical contamination within the wall cavities, and on the exposed =
surfaces downstairs. There will be a significant number of sample sites =
[tests] to be completed to be able to author a reliable report. After =
initial testing is completed, our intention is to apply restorative =
cleaning methods to targeted individual sample sites, followed by =
subsequent testing, post-cleaning, to provide data to measure the =
effectiveness of =
cleaning/decontamination.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">All samples taken from =
site will require laboratory analysis before being incorporated into a =
report. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=93 so we want =
to capture swab samples from surfaces before and after the =
decontamination process is =
undertaken.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">At this stage we are =
looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as well as CPEng =
site visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet be =
confirmed.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">I am unsure from your =
letter attached whether Raffaella and/or other nominated parties wish to =
be present while this testing and assessment is being conducted. Can you =
please confirm for me so that I can complete arrangements that will suit =
all parties who need to be =
present.</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div =
style=3D"margin: 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, =
sans-serif;"><span style=3D"font-size: 11pt;">Many =
Thanks,</span><o:p></o:p></div></div><div><div style=3D"margin: 0in; =
font-size: 12pt; font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><span =
